---
import NavBar from "../components/NavBar.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Game" description="Aria-7th Lab 的轻量 playroom。" bodyClass="inner-page">
  <NavBar compact />
  <main class="page-frame">
    <section class="page-hero glass-panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">GAME / PLAYROOM</p>
      <h1>Playroom</h1>
      <p>这里预留小游戏入口。首版先做成静态占位，后续可以加入 Canvas 小游戏或收藏清单。</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mini-game glass-panel" data-click-counter>
      <div class="counter-display">
        <span>today mood</span>
        <strong data-click-count>0</strong>
      </div>
      <button class="primary-button" type="button" data-click-button>收集一片花瓣</button>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
